-- MOVES-Sberbank hires Annie Jordan and Paul Goldfinch
-- 
-- Fri Sep 19, 2014 06:24AM EDT
-- None



Sept 19 (Reuters) - Corporate and investment banking business Sberbank CIB Ltd said it appointed Paul Goldfinch as chief financial officer and Annie Jordan as head of human resources, managing director.

Jordan will report to Alexander Bazarov, acting head of Sberbank CIB, and Goldfinch will report to Bazarov and Nikolay Tsekhomsky, director of Sberbank's financial department. Jordan will be responsible for the company's regular HR work and take an active part in key projects, and Goldfinch will be responsible for all aspects of the finance function within the company, Sberbank said.